title: Nest with Eggs
description:
A bird's nest with eggs inside.

May be used to talk about actual nests or birds. May also be used to talk about home in general or to represent phrases like nest egg or empty nest.

apple_vendor_description: Apple's nest with eggs emoji is a charming depiction of nature's bounty, featuring a softly woven nest with realistically rendered eggs nestled within its comforting embrace. On Apple devices, the texture of the twigs and straw is subtly defined through detailed shading and smooth gradients, giving it a tactile feel. The eggs themselves possess a delicate sheen, hinting at new life and beginnings, making this emoji a symbol of family, hope, and nurturing on Apple devices.
